Class RegistrationForm

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.model.RegistrationForm
public class RegistrationForm extends Object
RegistrationForm is a model class that represents the data submitted by a user during registration. It contains personal details such as name, email, date of birth, address, and phone number. This object is populated automatically when a user submits the registration form in the Thymeleaf view.
